{
  "texts": [
    "To verify this, we evaluated the fine-grained model's ability to predict the two-digit quality score by prompting it to continue generation after <boc>, and found that its predictions were highly accurate.",
    "We hypothesize that the model becomes overly focused on solving this auxiliary prediction task, which detracts from its ability to develop other skills that would improve downstream performance.",
    "To evaluate this hypothesis, we run the probing experiments described in Section 3.",
    "Results for predicting document topic and quality appear in Figure 6.",
    "In the left panel where the task is unrelated to the included metadata type (quality), the QS-coarse appended model outperforms the QS-fine appended model, especially in the early layers."
  ]
}